1) First run data_fil.py by typing "python data_fil.py" in terminal.
2) These will give you three csv files whose names are ratings.csv, movies.csv and users.csv. 

3) Next run content_based.py by typing "python content_based.py" in terminal which shows recommendation of movie based on method called content based filtering.
4) These command during it's running will ask the user to enter the movie name. Enter the movie which you watched last time and then according to it it will give recommendation of 10 movies.

a) Below is the first example in which first column gives movie index given in dataset and second column gives name of movie

